<i>another case there,</i>

00:16.854 --> 00:18.705
<i>in your dream.</i>

00:18.740 --> 00:20.974
<i>It all feels
completely real to me.</i>

00:21.009 --> 00:23.043
You can't tell whether
you're awake or asleep

00:23.077 --> 00:24.144
