01:45.943 --> 01:49.129
All I do is end up working
twice as many homicides.

01:49.163 --> 01:50.614
Bernard Mackenzie?

01:50.648 --> 01:52.432
The fertility doctor, you
guys never heard of him?

01:52.467 --> 01:54.334
40-year-old marathoner,

01:54.368 --> 01:56.286
and Tuesday he drops
dead of a heart attack.

01:56.320 --> 01:57.504
Autopsy report
comes back clean,

01:57.538 --> 01:58.988
but something about
it kept bugging me.

01:59.006 --> 02:01.174
So tonight I do a
