Olympian a heart attack,

02:10.017 --> 02:11.885
but it's usually
not very subtle,

02:11.936 --> 02:13.520
which is where this
guy's killer gets smart.

02:13.554 --> 02:15.222
The doctor here was diabetic,

02:15.273 --> 02:17.140
so they planted the
chemical in his insulin,

02:17.174 --> 02:18.325
pushes it out
of the blood,

02:18.359 --> 02:19.810
basically makes it untraceable.

02:19.844 --> 02:21.511
Unless you're really good,

02:21.529 --> 02:22.679
which I am.

02:22.697 --> 02:24.981
So, congratulations,
gentlemen,

02:25.015 --> 02:27.851
Dr. Bernard Mackenzie's death
is now officially a murder.

02:27.869 --> 02:30.320
Sorry.

02:30.354 --> 02:32.322
I thought there was more
in the fridge.

02:32.356 --> 02:33.874
I'll get to the store
tomorrow.

02:33.908 --> 02:35.208
It's fine.

02:35.243 --> 02:36.910
You know, I can
go out, or like,

02:36.961 --> 02:38.829
eat at Cole's when
you're going to be late.

02:38.863 --> 02:40.697
His dad said it's okay.

02:40.715 --> 02:42.382
What, you don't like cereal
and soda night?

