09:23.320 --> 09:26.456
Look, if it makes
you feel any better,

09:26.490 --> 09:28.658
no one ever rode it.

09:28.676 --> 09:31.694
It wasn't finished
when Rex,

09:35.499 --> 09:39.502
After that, I didn't really feel
